<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, November 16 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,308.16 on Monday, up
192.75 points, or 8.95 percent, from Friday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 58 trillion Turkish liras (over 196 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went up 251.6 points, or 9.35 percent to
close at 2,886.28 points. The industrial index rose 126.22
points, or 7.74 percent, to close at 1,736.21 points and the
service index climbed 224.34 points, or 7.46 percent, to close at
3,237.72 points. 
</P>
</TEXT>
