crisis, and this won us international appreciation," he added.
</P>
<P>
Bangladesh has so far received 756 million U.S. dollars of
donation from 38 countries and 43 donor agencies for relief and
post-flood rehabilitation and reconstruction programs, still short
of its targeted 880 million dollars' assistance. 
