<HEADLINE> Shanghai Baogang Group Company </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, November 17 (Xinhua) -- Baoshan Steel Complex merged
with the Shanghai Metallurgical Company and the Meishan Steel
Company to form the Shanghai Baogang Group Company in Shanghai
today.
</P>
<P>
Vice-Premier Wu Bangguo attended the opening ceremony and
called the new complex a "great event" in the iron and steel
industry. He urged it to become a first-class steel company with
first-rate products as requested by President Jiang Zemin.
</P>
