restructuring of state enterprises, Wu said, pointing out that
China has become the largest iron and steel products producer in
the world but it is not yet a powerful iron and steel manufacturer
because of a lack of efficiency and technology.
</P>
<P>
He said that the State Council has high hopes for the new
merger and asked the company to improve products, technology,
structure, and management and asked the city government to
continue its strong support for the steel giant. 
