<HEADLINE> Shanghai Opens First Private Drugstore </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, November 17 (Xinhua) -- The Fushoutang Pharmaceutical
Co. Ltd. recently opened to become the first private drugstore in
Shanghai, China's major commercial and financial center.
</P>
<P>
The original Fushoutang Drugstore of Traditional Chinese Herbal
Medicine was opened in 1582 by Gu Bangxian, a famous physician in
the Ming Dynasty (1368-1644).
</P>
<P>
Fushoutang Pharmaceutical President Gu Juan is a 14th
generation descendant of Gu Bangxian.
</P>
<P>
Gu, 70, is well-known for her traditional medical treatments for
cancer and leukemia. 
</P>
</TEXT>
