on the future development of China's high energy physics and other
issues of common concern.
</P>
<P>
Zhu welcomed the scientists who are here to attend the 19th
Meeting of the Sino-US Joint Committee on High Energy Physics. He
also praised the progress in Sino-US cooperation related to high
energy research.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese premier voiced appreciation for the important
contributions made by the scientists to Sino-US scientific
cooperation and the development of China's high energy physics.
</P>
