Halonen said her government will be head of the European Union
for the next term and Finland looks forward to broadening
relations with Iran as head of the Organization of the Islamic
Conference.
</P>
<P>
She also praised Khatami for his proposal designating the year
2001 "the year of dialogue between civilizations."
</P>
<P>
Halonen arrived here on Sunday for a two-day official
visit. 
</P>
